commitResults.messageBody:
Current Person attribute classes require each attribute to be populated
with information.

All attributes may not be available at time of insertion of contact.

Modify behavior such that attributes may be empty at time of insertion
of contact; allows contact to be created first and additional information
to be added later.

Let's,
* intergrate the GitHubProfile, Language classes into the Person class and
  modify the behavior of the Person class to allow late insertion of
  attribute information
* update the relevant tests to handle additional attributes, and changes
  to behavior

* update MESSAGE_USAGE to reflect changes to behavior, updates to Person
  class attributes

* update MESSAGE_USAGE to reflect updates to Person class attributes
* update createEditedPerson method to handle new attributes

* update parse command to handle new attribute prefixes, changes to
  behavior of "add" command

* update constants with prefixes of new attributes in Person class, "g/"
  for GitHubProfile attribute, "l/" for Language attribute

* update parse command to handle new attribute prefixes
